OL,3,CPlaid Cymru leader calls Senedd
OL,4,CElection a two-horse race with Reform
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru has said voters should
OL,7,F"choose hope" and vote for them on 7
OL,8,FMay, claiming the Senedd Election is a
OL,9,F"straight choice between Plaid and
OL,10,FReform".
OL,12,FIn a recent ITV Cymru Wales poll,
OL,13,FPlaid Cymru remained on course to be
OL,14,Fthe biggest party after polling day,
OL,15,Fwith Reform UK the second largest and
OL,16,FLabour third.
OL,18,FPlaid Cymru's leader Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,19,FMS was speaking at his party's
OL,20,Fcampaign launch in Bedwas, Caerphilly.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
