OL,3,CPlaid Cymru leader calls Senedd
OL,4,CElection a two-horse race with Reform
OL,6,FMr Iorwerth outlined the party's key
OL,7,Fpriorities for the election including
OL,8,Fcutting NHS waiting lists and speeding
OL,9,Fup treatment times, helping families
OL,10,Fwith #30,000 worth of free childcare,
OL,11,Fimproving educational standards and
OL,12,Ftackling child poverty.
OL,14,FPlaid Cymru said it would also create
OL,15,Fwell-paid jobs with a new plan to
OL,16,Fsupport Welsh business and stand up
OL,17,Ffor Wales to get a fair deal from
OL,18,FWestminster.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
