SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775131865
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru leader calls Senedd
OL,4,CElection a two-horse race with Reform
OL,6,FSpeaking at the launch on Monday (30
OL,7,FMarch), Mr Iorwerth said: "We will
OL,8,Fstand up for Wales to get a fair deal
OL,9,Ffrom Westminster. May 7 is a historic
OL,10,Fopportunity to change Wales for the
OL,11,Fbetter.
OL,13,F"Labour's time is up ` they are now
OL,14,Fout of the picture. This campaign is a
OL,15,Fstraight choice between Plaid Cymru
OL,16,Fand Reform, between hope and division,
OL,17,Fbetween credibility and chaos.
OL,26,@oD@[OUuD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,469,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775131865
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru leader calls Senedd
OL,4,CElection a two-horse race with Reform
OL,6,F"Plaid Cymru is the only party with an
OL,7,Fambitious and deliverable plan to
OL,8,Fbring down those waiting times, to
OL,9,Fraise education standards, to support
OL,10,Ffamilies with that universal childcare
OL,11,Foffer, to support businesses and the
OL,12,FWelsh high streets, giving them the
OL,13,Fbacking that they deserve.
OL,15,FPlaid launched its campaign in
OL,16,FCaerphilly ` the scene of its Senedd
OL,17,Fby-election victory against Labour
OL,18,Flast year.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
