PN,46805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775131865
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru leader calls Senedd
OL,4,CElection a two-horse race with Reform
OL,6,F"We return here for the launch of our
OL,7,Felection campaign to the constituency
OL,8,Fof Caerphilly where history was made
OL,9,Ffive months ago," Mr ap Iorwerth said.
OL,11,F"Five weeks from now Wales can make
OL,12,Fhistory again and that spirit of
OL,13,FCaerphilly 2025 can be the spirit that
OL,14,Fdrives us forward to the formation of
OL,15,Fthe first ever Plaid Cymru government
OL,16,Ffor Wales on May 7."
OL,18,FHe said that Lindsay Whittle's by-
OL,19,Felection win in Caerphilly in October
OL,20,Flast year could be a "blueprint for
OL,21,Fsuccess in all parts of Wales".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]sD@AOU|D@VOU}D@^O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
