PN,46806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775131865
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru leader calls Senedd
OL,4,CElection a two-horse race with Reform
OL,6,FHe added: "Plaid Cymru's message for
OL,7,Fthe next five weeks to the people of
OL,8,FWales is this: Choose hope. Twenty-
OL,9,Fseven years of Labour leadership in
OL,10,FWales has held Wales back.
OL,12,F"I have no doubt that our nation has
OL,13,Fso much untapped potential, and if we
OL,14,Fhave the honour of leading Welsh
OL,15,FGovernment for the next four years, we
OL,16,Fare determined in Plaid Cymru to
OL,17,Funleash it.
OL,19,F"We in no doubt, this is the most
OL,20,Fimportant election in the history of
OL,21,Fdevolution.
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
