PN,46807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F468A1775131865
OL,3,CPlaid Cymru leader calls Senedd
OL,4,CElection a two-horse race with Reform
OL,6,F"I am urging the people of Wales to
OL,7,Funite behind Plaid Cymru for the
OL,8,Fchance of a Government that stands up
OL,9,Ffor Wales in a way we have never seen
OL,10,Fbefore.
OL,12,F"May 7 is an opportunity to choose new
OL,13,Fbeginnings for Wales, new ideas, a new
OL,14,Fenergy, a higher level of ambition
OL,15,Fthan ever before."
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
